### 쿠폰 템플릿 등록 - 정액(FIXED)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

{
  "name": "신규가입 3천원",
  "type": "FIXED",
  "value": 3000,
  "minOrderAmount": 10000,
  "expiredAt": "2030-12-31T23:59:59+09:00"
}

### 쿠폰 템플릿 등록 - 정률(RATE)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

{
  "name": "정률 10%",
  "type": "RATE",
  "value": 10,
  "expiredAt": "2030-12-31T23:59:59+09:00"
}

### 쿠폰 템플릿 등록 - 검증 실패 (정률 > 100, 400)
