Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

{
  "name": "잘못된 정률",
  "type": "RATE",
  "value": 150,
  "expiredAt": "2030-12-31T23:59:59+09:00"
}

### 쿠폰 템플릿 등록 - admin 헤더 없음 (401)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "권한 없음",
  "type": "FIXED",
  "value": 1000,
