}

### 쿠폰 템플릿 단건 조회
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/1
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

### 쿠폰 템플릿 단건 조회 - 존재하지 않는 id (404)
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/9999
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

### 쿠폰 템플릿 목록 조회 (페이지)
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons?page=0&size=20
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

### 쿠폰 템플릿 수정
PUT {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

{
  "name": "정률 15%",
  "type": "RATE",
  "value": 15,
  "minOrderAmount": 20000,
  "expiredAt": "2031-06-30T23:59:59+09:00"
}

### 쿠폰 템플릿 삭제 (soft delete)
DELETE {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/1
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

### 쿠폰 템플릿 삭제 - 존재하지 않는 id (404)
DELETE {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/9999
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

### 쿠폰 발급 내역 조회 (페이지)
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/1/issues?page=0&size=20
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1

### 쿠폰 발급 내역 조회 - 존재하지 않는 템플릿 (404)
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/9999/issues
X-Loopers-Admin-Id: admin-1
